PN,31901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FDoctors have praised "unprecedentedly
OL,7,Fstrong responses" to an injection that
OL,8,Feradicated entire tumours in otherwise
OL,9,Ftreatment- resistant cancer cases
OL,10,Fduring a trial.
OL,12,FThe injection shrank the tumours for
OL,13,F42% of patients, according to an
OL,14,Finternational study by the Institute
OL,15,Fof Cancer Research (ICR), London.
OL,17,FScientists gave amivantamab to people
OL,18,Fwith recurrent and/or metastatic head
OL,19,Fand neck cancer that had stopped
OL,20,Fresponding to standard treatments.
OL,26,@nD@VOUoD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
