FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FAmivantamab is a small injection,
OL,7,Funlike many cancer medications that
OL,8,Frequire intravenous drips.
OL,10,FOne participant with tongue cancer
OL,11,Fsaid the treatment reduced his pain
OL,12,Fand swelling, and he is no longer
OL,13,Fexperiencing the "life-impacting" side
OL,14,Feffects he had during chemotherapy.
OL,26,@uD@ROUuD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FProfessor Kevin Harrington, professor
OL,7,Fin biological cancer therapies at the
OL,8,Finstitute and consultant oncologist at
OL,9,FThe Royal Marsden NHS Foundation
OL,10,FTrust, said: "These are
OL,11,Funprecedentedly strong responses in
OL,12,Fpatients whose disease has become
OL,13,Fresistant to both chemotherapy and
OL,14,Fimmunotherapy.
OL,16,F"This is a group of patients for whom
OL,17,Ftreatment options are extremely
OL,18,Flimited, so seeing this level of
OL,19,Fbenefit is very striking."
OL,26,@rD@NOUxD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FHe added: "This treatment has the
OL,7,Fpotential to benefit many thousands of
OL,8,Fpatients each year."
OL,10,FHead and neck cancer is the sixth most
OL,11,Fcommon cancer worldwide, and it
OL,12,Faffects around 12,800 people in the UK
OL,13,Feach year.
OL,15,FThis phase of the OrigAMI-4 trial
OL,16,Flooked at 102 people with recurrent or
OL,17,Fmetastatic head and neck squamous cell
OL,18,Fcarcinoma (HNSCC), whose cancer had
OL,19,Fcontinued to grow despite
OL,20,Fimmunotherapy and platinum-based
OL,21,Fchemotherapy.
OL,26,@nD@KOUpD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FThe patients, from 55 hospitals in 11
OL,7,Fcountries, only received amivantamab,
OL,8,Fwhich is being developed by Johnson &
OL,9,FJohnson.
OL,11,FTumours shrank in 43 participants ` 15
OL,12,Fhad them disappear completely and 28
OL,13,Fsaw their tumours shrink significantly.
OL,15,FPatients with amivantamab lived for a
OL,16,Fmedian of 12.5 months after starting
OL,17,Fthe treatment, despite having a cancer
OL,18,Ftype with "very poor outcomes" once
OL,19,Fstandard treatments stop working, the
OL,20,FICR said.
OL,26,@zD@KOUzD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
