FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FTumours started to respond within
OL,7,Fabout six weeks and patients had a
OL,8,Fmedian of a little more than six-and-a-
OL,9,Fhalf months before the cancer started
OL,10,Fto grow again, it found.
OL,12,FCarl Walsh, 56, from Birmingham, was
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with tongue cancer in May
OL,14,F2024 and joined the study at The Royal
OL,15,FMarsden in July 2025 after
OL,16,Fchemotherapy and immunotherapy were
OL,17,Fboth unsuccessful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
