FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FIn a statement released by the ICR
OL,7,Fduring his 17th treatment cycle, he
OL,8,Fsaid: "I now feel able to live a
OL,9,Fnormal life. Before starting the
OL,10,Ftrial, I struggled to speak properly
OL,11,Fand found eating difficult because of
OL,12,Fthe swelling and pain.
OL,14,F"Since beginning treatment, the
OL,15,Fswelling has reduced significantly,
OL,16,Fand my pain levels have improved
OL,17,Fconsiderably.
OL,19,F"I'm also no longer experiencing the
OL,20,Fsame life-impacting side effects that
OL,21,FI had during chemotherapy."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU{D@AOU}D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
