PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe drug is called a bispecific
OL,12,Fmonoclonal antibody and it blocks two
OL,13,Fsignals: EGFR (Epidermal Growth Factor
OL,14,FReceptor), which is a protein that
OL,15,Fhelps tumours grow, and MET, a
OL,16,Fseparate pathway often used by cancer
OL,17,Fcells to escape treatment.
OL,19,FIt also has a third benefit: helping
OL,20,Fto activate the immune system to
OL,21,Fattack the tumour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FAs it is an injection, it is faster,
OL,7,Fmore convenient for patients, and
OL,8,F"significantly easier" to deliver in
OL,9,Foutpatient clinics, the ICR said.
OL,11,FAmivantamab is given every three weeks
OL,12,Fand side effects were mild to moderate.
OL,14,FFewer than ten patients stopped
OL,15,Ftreatment because of side effects.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
