FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FProfessor Kristian Helin, chief
OL,7,Fexecutive of the ICR, said: "This
OL,8,Fstudy demonstrates how the development
OL,9,Fof new treatments through rigorous
OL,10,Fcancer research may lead to meaningful
OL,11,Fadvances, even for patients with very
OL,12,Flimited treatment options.
OL,14,F"Achieving this level of tumour
OL,15,Fresponse and encouraging survival
OL,16,Foutcomes in such a challenging to
OL,17,Ftreat group represents a significant
OL,18,Fstep forward."
OL,26,@oD@]OUvD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1780319468
OL,3,CCancer jab destroys whole tumours in
OL,4,Ctreatment-resistant cases, trial shows
OL,6,FAmivantamab has already been approved
OL,7,Ffor multiple subtypes of lung cancer
OL,8,Facross multiple lines of therapy.
OL,10,FThe study excluded patients who had
OL,11,Fhuman papillomavirus (HPV) positive
OL,12,Foropharyngeal squamous cell carcinoma.
OL,14,FHead and neck cancers that are not
OL,15,Fcaused by HPV are usually harder to
OL,16,Ftreat and have poorer responses to
OL,17,Fstandard therapy, ICR said.
OL,19,F"Making progress in this group
OL,20,Fparticularly important," the institute
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
